Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D5024283%26sensormode%3DN%26highlight_id%3D228121&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=c4a482db\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5024283&amp;sensormode=N&amp;highlight_id=228121</a><br />\n<br />\n[魚蛋論] 點解以前唔向中國移動執法???<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5021328&amp;sensormode=N&amp;highlight_id=228121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D5021328%26sensormode%3DN%26highlight_id%3D228121&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=f949b27e\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5021328&amp;sensormode=N&amp;highlight_id=228121</a><br />\n<br />\n[龍門系列] 相對於 香港人 同 新香港人<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5013720&amp;sensormode=N&amp;page=1&amp;highlight_id=228121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D5013720%26sensormode%3DN%26page%3D1%26highlight_id%3D228121&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=7c010185\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=5013720&amp;sensormode=N&amp;page=1&amp;highlight_id=228121</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會員編號: 228121<br />\n膠名: Sky Croc<br />\n加入日期: 8/10/2009<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum.hkgolden.com/ProfilePage.aspx?userid=228121\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2FProfilePage.aspx%3Fuserid%3D228121&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=fec405e7\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum.hkgolden.com/ProfilePage.aspx?userid=228121</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>佢幾年前就開始特登打簡體<br />\n<br />\n睇佢D語氣同用字同香港人一樣<br />\n<br />\n我諗佢係特登咁做，引人屌柒佢<br />\n<br />\n我諗佢係用心良苦，時時刻刻等人屌柒簡體<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係既話我屌佢全家</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"limegreen\">支那仔確認</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\